dct_title_s: Eastern archipelago, Java eastern portion including Madura, Bali and Lombok
dct_alternative_sm: Java eastern portion including Madura, Bali and Lombok
dct_description_sm: Nautical chart of eastern Java, islands of Bali and Lombok. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depth shown by bathymetric soundings.
In lower left margin: B.A. small corrections 1934-761-1716 ... 1941-1229-1487. From H.O.N.M. '39-8, 34 ... '41-52 ('42-2, 8. Printed by H.O. Dec. '41, Apr. '42.
In upper left margin: Hydrographic Office, U.S. Navy emergency reproduction of B.A. chart.
"Reproduced by the U.S. Hydrographic Office from British Admiralty chart with the permission of the Controller, H.M. Stationery Office and Hydrographer of the Royal Navy."
dct_publisher_sm: Published at the Admiralty, 18th Jan. 1934, under the superintendence of Captain J.A. Edgell, O.B.E.R.N. Hydrographer
